cebook, Instagram, LinkedIn campaigns. Optimized for conversions.</p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700\">\n                        <li><i class=\"fas fa-check text-orange-600 mr-2\"></i>Google Ads</li>\n                        <li><i class=\"fas fa-check text-orange-600 mr-2\"></i>Social ads</li>\n                        <li><i class=\"fas fa-check text-orange-600 mr-2\"></i>Retargeting</li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-200 hover:border-orange-500 transition\">\n                    <div class=\"w-12 h-12 gradient-forge rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-share-alt text-white text-xl\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">Social Media</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-6\">Content creation, community management, influencer partnerships. Brand growth.</p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700\">\n                        <li><i class=\"fas fa-check text-orange-600 mr-2\"></i>Content calendar</li>\n                        <li><i class=\"fas fa-check text-orange-600 mr-2\"></i>Community mgmt</li>\n                        <li><i class=\"fas fa-check text-orange-600 mr-2\"></i>Analytics</li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-200 hover:border-orange-500 transition\">\n                    <div class=\"w-12 h-12 gradient-forge rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-envelope text-white text-xl\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">Email Marketing</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-6\">Campaigns, automation, segmentation. High conversion rates and engagement.</p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700\">\n                        <li><i class=\"fas fa-check text-orange-600 mr-2\"></i>Campaign design</li>\n                        <li><i class=\"fas fa-check text-orange-600 mr-2\"></i>Automation</li>\n                        <li><i class=\"fas fa-check text-orange-600 mr-2\"></i>A/B testing</li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-200 hover:border-orange-500 transition\">\n                    <div class=\"w-12 h-12 gradient-forge rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-chart-bar text-white text-xl\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">Analytics & Reporting</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-6\">Data analysis, performance tracking, insights, and strategic recommendations.</p>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700\">\n                        <li><i class=\"fas fa-check text-orange-600 mr-2\"></i>GA4 setup</li>\n                        <li><i class=\"fas fa-check text-orange-600 mr-2\"></i>Monthly reports</li>\n                        <li><i class=\"fas fa-check text-orange-600 mr-2\"></i>Optimization</li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-200 hover:border-orange-500 transition\">\n                    <div class=\"w-12 h-12 gradient-forge rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-strategy text-white text-xl\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">Strategy & Consulting</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-6\">Market analysis, competitor research, growth planning, brand 